Love the property!  Centrally located and gorgeous grounds, friendly staff and I love Frank Lloyd Weight architecture.   We have stayed in the villas several times. Standard rooms once or twice. In the villas it is best to request that you stay in a renovated property in order that you get the true Waldorf Astoria experience. Older villas can be a bit disappointing, but staff is always happy to get us into a renovated room upon request.  Life happens and even when small issues come up the Biltmore staff is happy and prompt to help make the stay enjoyable. Bring your family and enjoy!

