What a fun, well designed concept.  I came in just before 10am on a weekday with my kids.  There was an impressive amount of people eating & we know why... This breakfast joint is solid. The veggie omelette was a good size for me, but may be a tad small for more aggressive eaters. The kids pancakes were super big... At 3.99 a great deal.   The food was a bit over saturated with butter from cooking, but I'm giving the kitchen staff a break with 4 stars as I know they will hit their rhythm soon and this place will be packed. With decent parking and a cool modern vibe I definitely recommend it.

